graph TD
    A[User] -->|Clicks Continue with GitHub| B(GitHub OAuth Login)
    B -->|Authenticates| C{Select Repository}
    C -->|Connects Repo| D[System Clones/Fetches Repo Data]

    D --> E{Choose Action}

    E -->|Analyze Codebase| F[Code Analysis Engine]
    F --> F1[Structure Overview]
    F --> F2[Tech Stack Detection]
    F --> F3[Complexity Metrics]
    
    E -->|Chat with Codebase| G[LLM Chat Interface]
    G --> G1[Ask Questions about Code]
    G --> G2[Get Explanations / Suggestions]

    E -->|Analytics| H[Repo Analytics Dashboard]
    H --> H1[Commit Activity]
    H --> H2[Contributor Stats]
    H --> H3[File Change Frequency]

    E -->|Security Scan| I[Security Checker]
    I --> I1[Vulnerability Scan]
    I --> I2[Secrets/Keys Detection]
    I --> I3[Dependency Audit]

    E -->|Error Logging| J[Error Logging System]
    J --> J1[Runtime Error Aggregation]
    J --> J2[Log Visualization]
    J --> J3[Alert Rules]

    F --> K{Check NPM Package}
    G --> K
    H --> K
    I --> K
    J --> K

    K -->|If not installed| L[Prompt: Install via NPM?]
    L -->|User confirms| M[Run NPM Install]
    M --> N[Ensure Required Tools Available]
    
    K -->|Already installed| N
    N --> O[All Features Ready]
    O --> P[User Continues Workflow]